  "description": "Get ready to dive into a magical visual novel adventure under the sea!\n\nLyra is a very special little mermaid: she has the power to sense the emotions of others... and transform them into light! When mysterious dark areas begin to spread across the ocean, filling it with sadness, Lyra decides to take action. With the help of a group of unique and fun friends—including synchronised seahorses, a grumpy octopus, and a very absent-minded lanternfish—she will embark on an exciting mission to save Aqua-topia and restore joy to its inhabitants.\n\nA story full of tenderness, laughter, adventure, and moments to learn how to take care of oneself and others.\n\nIncludes:\n\nLots of full-colour backgrounds, full of underwater details.\n\nAdorable characters that little ones will love.\n\nImmersive music accompanies each scene.\n\nA beautiful, magical, and value-filled story, perfect for children.",
